  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HELLFIRE RAMPAGE VR</strong> is an action-based combat game that blends shooting and melee fighting mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a genius portal inventor who has detected an abnormal signal from another world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After investigating, you discover that hellish creatures are collecting magical crystal essences and preparing to invade the HUMANITY</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> YOUR MISSION IS TO STOP THEIR INVASION AND COLLECT THE CRYSTALS !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your <strong>ability</strong> to <strong>slow time</strong> and take on powerful enemies in intense battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>[BULLET TIME</i></strong> + <strong><i>DASH]</i></strong> is a toxic combination for tactical movements and survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> REFLECT BULLETS BACK BY RICOCHET</strong> <strong>WITH ANY WEAPON</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine a magic wand with a talisman or a shotgun with a sickle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launch fireballs, swing a lightsaber, throw shurikens, or even play a demonic kalimba. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The arsenal is packed with epic gear, from chainsaws to crossbows and beyond!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get ready to test around 30+ non-trivial guns!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face dangerous hordes and  destroy their source.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to meet skeletons, imps, demons, hellhounds and mad ravens, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >undead summon kings, skull queens, giant devils, toxic moths and others...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/414a253ce680ab4cbe84eb48edf82824.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> HELL CREATURES WILL NOT LET YOU TO GET BORED!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most thrilling and intense fights are waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around <strong>70+</strong> challenges from different mysterious locations</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> GET READY TO SWEAT IN MORTAL CHALLENGES</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Are you brave enough to challenge the <strong>HELL</strong>?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HELLFIRE RAMPAGE VR</strong> is an action-based combat game that blends shooting and melee fighting mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a genius portal inventor who has detected an abnormal signal from another world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After investigating, you discover that hellish creatures are collecting magical crystal essences and preparing to invade the HUMANITY</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> YOUR MISSION IS TO STOP THEIR INVASION AND COLLECT THE CRYSTALS !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your <strong>ability</strong> to <strong>slow time</strong> and take on powerful enemies in intense battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>[BULLET TIME</i></strong> + <strong><i>DASH]</i></strong> is a toxic combination for tactical movements and survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-> REFLECT BULLETS BACK BY RICOCHET</strong> <strong>WITH ANY WEAPON</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor